TextArea_SetFont
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<Window=>window/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Veneer:	<textarea_set_font>
Syntax:	TextArea_SetFont
#indent

On Entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = window object Id
r2 = 0x4018 + 8 (16416)
r3 = gadget component Id
r4 = font handle
r5 = font width
r6 = font height
{f}
#indent
On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r1-r9 preserved
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method sets the font in the TextArea.